GTMetrix,is,a,tool,to,test,the,speed,and,performance,of,websites,GTMetrix,also,provides,a,list,of,recommended,actions,for,developers,to,make,their,websites,faster,such,as,avoiding,bad,URLs,and,specifying,image,dimensions,The,GTMetrix,REST,API,allows,developers,to,build,their,own,testing,and,performance,tools,based,on,GTMetrix